{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I will kick as many goals as I can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "However, I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I belong to, to that side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and I have more evenly started to distribute my-- my time, my social orientations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's when we formed a little club, which, incidentally at the time, had it been officially known, would have been a no-no.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because there's no socially-- no organization clubs were possible in those times for political reasons, anti-establishment reasons, and of course, Jewish reasons.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we had our little social clubs which consisted of eight boys from the class, which happened to be all Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's where my social life from the age of 16, 17, was, was concentrated on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, of course I do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember all eight of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Would, would you like to know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I know all eight of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The eight boys involved the-- out of the eight boys, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Fodor Laci, he died during the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in Bor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was in, in, in-- you-- have you heard of the labor camp in Bor, B-O-R--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in-- in Yugoslavia?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very famous, or infamous, labor camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He died there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bern Micky was with with, who is now in Los Angeles, whom I regularly visit if I'm there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Three are in Israel-- Orany Piszta, Polag Sanyi, and Weiner Dzuri.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very interesting that these boys, whom I also visit when I go there-- last time, we had a very interesting meeting in which we more or less, you know, drew balances of our lives, what we have done.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- obviously they went there because they're ardent Zionists.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "However, they have their share of disappointments, which I was personally very sorry to see.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
